TalendProperties:Property.label: ETL_Process
TalendProperties:Property.purpose: Data Integration and Preprocessing for Analytics
TalendProperties:Property.description:
The job is designed to integrate multiple data sources for a hotel reservation system.
It involves reading data from several CSV files, in which each representing different dimensions of the reservation system.
It then continues with extraction of a date dimension from the reservation fact table, followed by a merging process where all dimension tables are joined with the reservation fact table using their respective IDs.
The outcome is a consolidated CSV file that contains all information for further analysis in SAS Enterprise Miner after saving the file locally.
